com.nokia.maps.kml

Interface PlaceMark

  • All Superinterfaces:
    Feature

    public interface PlaceMark
extends Feature
    This class represents the <Placemark> tag from KML specification. A Placemark is a Feature with associated Geometry.

    • Field Summary
